Author: Pgkxhs2
Text: I binged nonstop for a few days and gained back all my progress from the past month or so. Tons of guilt. I just told myself that it was in the past, I cannot change it, and making myself feel bad about it doesn't help any. Afterall I don't think about my binges from a year ago. I started tracking again and within a couple days I feel great! Best of luck to you in whatever you decide to do!
